  <div class="sb_box br-bg">
    <h3 class="right_title">
      <div class="position">当前位置：<a href="/" title="首页">首页</a> &gt; <a href="/about/?2.html">潍博之信</a>&gt; <a href="/list/?3_1.html">规章制度</a></div>
      <span>规章制度</span> </h3>
    <div class="clear"></div>
    <div class="active" id="shownews">
      <h1 class="title">第十五章  考勤制度</h1>
      <div class="editor"><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第一条</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">考勤规定</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">一、上下班时间</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1、早晨，须提前十五分钟进馆打卡，其他上下班时间按规定执行。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2、严格按照本馆考勤细则执行。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">二、迟到、早退</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1、晚于上班时间15分钟为迟到、早于下班时间15分钟为早退。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2、因馆工作需要外出办公，须填写外出办公单，经分管馆长批准，否则按迟到、早退或旷工处理。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">三、旷工</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1、上班迟到超过1小时、下班早退超过1小时，又未请假者视为旷工。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2、无故不参加馆内组织的集体活动或会议视为旷工。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3、连续旷工15天；全年累计30天，按国家规定，视为自动离职。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">四、病假</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">请病假月累计</span>10天及以上者，急症、重病须住院治疗累计满30天及以上者，按规定扣除相应绩效工资。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">五、事假</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1、请假不足2小时者，累计2次视为半天；请假超过2小时，不足半天者，累计2次视为1天。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2、事假1天及以上者，按规定扣除相应绩效工资。</span></p><p style="text-indent:9px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3、集体活动或会议请假，按事假执行。</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第二条</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">请假规定</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:38px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">任何病假、事假须先以累计的公休、加班逐次抵消，无公休、加班可抵消时，方可请病假、事假；原则上禁止电话请假，如有特殊情况电话请假，假期结束后必须及时补交请假单。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">一、事假</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:9px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>1）半天以下，由科室主任批准。</span></p><p style="text-indent:9px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>2）1天及以上，3天以下由分管馆长批准。</span></p><p style="text-indent:9px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>3）3天及以上由馆长批准。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>4）中层人员（正职）请假1天及以上由馆长批准。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>5）请假须填写请假单，逐级审批。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>6）公休假、婚假、产假请假，须提前提出申请。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">二、病假</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>1）3天以下由分管馆长批准。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>2）3天及以上由馆长批准。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>3）一般性疾病，可批准3天以内假期，最长可延至7天。如需继续治疗病休，可持正规医院病休单，按程序报馆长批准生效。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3、请假单由科室暂存，每月与考勤表一并汇总上报至办公室；</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4、公休假、节假日、婚丧假、产假按国家文件规定执行，同时根据馆内工作实际情况需要进行调整。</span></p><p style="text-indent:38px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">5、如有特殊情况，按相关规定具体处理。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">三、奖惩办法</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1、考勤由各科室自考为主。展区由保卫科负责考勤，严格执行考勤制度，禁止弄虚作假。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2、办公室负责全馆考勤情况监督、汇总。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3、各科室每月28日，将考勤请假汇总表，报办公室核实、汇总，经馆长审查后存档。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4、成立在岗抽查小组，由政工人员不定期对职工在岗情况进行抽查，每周至少二次。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;5、抽查时不在岗，又没有请假条者，视为空岗，每月超过2次，年内超过10次者，取消年底评优资格。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;6、每季度在公示栏上对请假、抽查情况进行公示。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;7、请事假每月超过4天，一年内累计超过15天者，取消年底评优资格。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;8、未尽事宜按国家规定执行。 </span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第三条</span> </span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">加班规定</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:38px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">为进一步规范加班管理，明确加班审批程序，构建有序的工作环境，现结合我馆实际就加班事宜作如下规定。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一、基本规定</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">为提高工作效率，鼓励员工在工作时间内完成应完成的工作。正常性工作加班的，原则上不填写加班单。上级临时交办任务且需非工作时间完成的，可视为加班。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">二、不视为加班的情况</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:38px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">1</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、利用非工作时间完成在工作时间内未完成的工作任务的。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:19px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;2</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、参加在非工作日组织的各种集体活动。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;3</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、参加在非工作日组织的各类学习培训。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:38px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">4</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、工作日或非工作日因公出差的。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;5</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、未经科室负责人、分管领导或局长指派或同意的工作时间的延长。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:38px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">三、审批流程</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">根据领导及工作安排，确需加班人员。要提前半天填写《加班申请单》，注明加班人姓名，事由，时间。报请部门负责人及分管领导签字后生效并报办公室备案。没有按规定办理相关手续的，加班视为无效。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">四、其他</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;1</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、加班应正常指纹考勤，否则不计加班时间（领导另有安排的除外）。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;2</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、加班按天计算，半天：（</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">4</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">小时以上），一天：（</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">8</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">小时以上），不能累计。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;3</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、加班予以补休，也可用于抵病假、事假，但只限当年。如有特殊情况，经馆长批准后可作跨年使用。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;4</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、补休以不影响本职工作为前提。</span></span></p><p><br/></p><script src="/inc/AspCms_VisitsAdd.asp?id=465"></script></div>
      
